Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.89,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.26,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:17.40,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.80,Gold,Roger,0,0,0,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:22.80,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:53.02,Main,Right Minster,0,0,0,,Those terrifying commanders...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.57,Main,Right Minster,0,0,0,,didn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.13,Main,Right Minster,0,0,0,,Just how strong are these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.72,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.14,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Look out below!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.80,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,This is gonna be dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.24,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Wadatsumi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.83,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,falling on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.95,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,You should've dropped him further away,\Nyou clumsy cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.68,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Shut it!  Or else I'll drop him on your head next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:11.60,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:18.41,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey, Chopper!  Shrink down a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:21.17,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You're making my giant robot look small!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.65,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Franky, that beam was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:27.80,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Was that robot actually good for anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:32.76,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:33.85,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.54,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Please wear a miniskirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.42,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:46.05,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Exactly what I'd expect from Luffy-kun's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:47.29,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.65,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,The N-Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:02.25,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,The Noah is almost on top of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.17,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.45,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,The island's gonna be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.60,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,If we hang around for too long,\Nthe Neptune Army's gonna trap us in the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.63,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Hurry!  Those insane commanders are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:20.87,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.16,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Is it too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.74,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Didn't it work... Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.38,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:44.61,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,He still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.64,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,isn't giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.54,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:03.33,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,is doing all he can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.48,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,to destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.16,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.09,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.05,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,If he can destroy the Noah before it crashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:23.86,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,then the island will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.98,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,But if he can't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.54,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,Fishman Island will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.63,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Show us what you can do, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.07,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:38.18,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.59,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.57,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.79,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to do it, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:07:00.18,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, Straw Hat!  We're cheering for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.29,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.35,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're human, yet you're fighting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.17,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're not gonna run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:11.14,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang in there, Big Brother Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:17.22,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fishman Island is in your hands now, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.55,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.70,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}We believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.33,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.51,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.91,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:42.89,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.61,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop! Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.96,0:07:49.31,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:58.24,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.05,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Your wounds are opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:04.82,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.49,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Watch from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.36,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Right now, I gotta put everything I got\Ninto destroying this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:20.93,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop right there, ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:34.47,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Father, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:39.64,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,We must destroy the Noah.  There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.72,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.19,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,It's the ship of promise... {Same phrasing as in 558}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:47.65,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,but we have no other choice. Our lives are more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:52.68,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Forgive us.  It looks like\Nwe won't be able to keep our promise -jamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.35,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Joyboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.81,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.06,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.49,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:13.47,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!  I beg of you, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get out of my way, Weak-hoshi!\NIf I don't destroy it, the island's gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:23.20,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.58,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Of course it's not!  Everyone's still on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.82,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Noah has already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.06,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.21,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Sea Kings?  Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:52.15,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama yelled at me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, this is no time to worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:03.48,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,I don't understand it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.50,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.97,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,the Noah has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.18,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:18.18,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,What's going on?  The Sea Kings stopped the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:28.05,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!  Your wounds have opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.65,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,You're covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:37.35,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,W-Well... whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:42.30,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,As long as... the ship stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:49.22,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm just glad... everyone's... safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.17,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.45,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:08.34,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,My, what a remarkable human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:12.31,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,What a strong human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:16.68,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Even if we'd been late,\Nthe island might have still been saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:20.25,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,but the Noah would have been completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:31.25,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we made it.\NGood thing Princess Shirahoshi called us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:36.13,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything... I was so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:42.03,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,That's not true.  You were touched\Nby the Straw Hat child's strong emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.36,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,and you made a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:51.38,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,An impassioned wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:57.18,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,that you could help him save the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:16.43,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Our power is your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:20.78,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,You summoned us to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.99,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,A-Attention everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:37.67,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,T-This is unbelievable.\NIt'd take too long to explain it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:40.95,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,but it's the undeniable truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.19,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,The Noah has stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.90,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,It wasn't completely destroyed either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:56.61,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Fishman Island... has been saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.98,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Straw Hat did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.39,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:37.84,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,We've waited a long time for you to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.59,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:44.25,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,This ship was built so we could pull it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:49.45,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,The tale of the ship has been passed down since the old times, so that we may do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:53.17,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Is that why the Noah is so big?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:53.97,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:14:01.91,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Once every couple hundred years,\Nour king is born into the body of one of the merfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.70,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.43,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Why indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.18,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.45,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Ever since you have been born,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.51,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,you have been our Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.43,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Honorable brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:24.78,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,Yeah... Shirahoshi... She can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:28.75,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,She must be speaking with the Sea Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:29.76,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:34.87,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Several Sea Kings\Nsuddenly appeared outside of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.73,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Almost as if to stop Luffy-san from destroying the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.81,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,They came to protect it.\NThat's what it looks like, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:47.65,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Perhaps the Noah is somehow important to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.43,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.19,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,The Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.65,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,So, it's finally awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:01.31,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,The power that could destroy the world itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:08.38,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Look.  The bubble is being absorbed by the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:11.95,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Humans can't survive on the ocean floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:15.31,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.82,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:19.74,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.50,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Perhaps I was imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:35.91,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,That human with the hat.  He heard our voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.77,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,He couldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:43.19,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,This happened before, a little while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:46.00,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Yes, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:51.05,Flashbacks,Roger,0,0,0,,Rayleigh, did you hear that voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.37,Flashbacks,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:54.56,Flashbacks,Rayleigh,0,0,0,,We're in the complete silence of the deep sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:16:00.06,Flashbacks,Roger,0,0,0,,Who's there?!  Who's talking so far underwater?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.81,Flashbacks,Roger,0,0,0,,Hey!  Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.98,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.27,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Why indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:20.38,Main,Den,0,0,0,,S-Sea Kings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:23.51,Main,Hachi,0,0,0,,T-They're carrying the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.48,Main,Caimie,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're gonna eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.80,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,The ship is badly damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:38.70,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Can it be fixed?  Can it still still serve its purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.48,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:46.38,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,To fix it, we'd need the skills of that clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:49.08,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,but times have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.72,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Can it be fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.61,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,Hopefully it will be fixed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:59.02,Main,Sea King,0,0,0,,before the promised time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.05,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,This is Ryuuguu Palace!  Come in, Left Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:08.45,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,We have an urgent report for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:09.43,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:12.75,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,The mermaids who were kidnapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:15.73,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,have been found inside of the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:19.56,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,What?!  So, are they alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:23.35,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Yes.  They're a little dazed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.73,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,but they say they can\Nremember the face of their captor clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:30.30,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the treasure room\Nwas found empty at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:34.09,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,There isn't anything left at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:37.59,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Of course, this includes\Nthe national treasure, the Tamate Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.96,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:45.34,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,It appears someone has robbed us\Nwhile we were away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:48.91,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Never mind some petty thief stealing treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:53.72,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,We could have lost the entire country\Njust now -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:59.66,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,More importantly,\Ntell everybody that the girls are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:04.21,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,It might be a little late, but we must show that the Straw Hats are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.74,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,We've done something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:16.30,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,If anyone tries to use bubbles to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.34,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I'll shoot them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.98,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:23.55,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Have mercy, Boss!  Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:26.10,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,I was just scared of Hody and his bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.88,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,We can go, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.54,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,We don't have anything to do with\Nthe conflict on this island!  We're just humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:35.53,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,This island depends on tourism and\Nthe money it gets from human pirate visitors, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.57,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:41.76,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I never said that we'd kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.42,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Wait for the Neptune Royal Family's judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:53.30,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,This is an announcement for all citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.47,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,The Straw Hat Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:19:00.11,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,had no involvement in the kidnapping of the mermaids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:07.29,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,We admit that we did not check the facts properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:11.84,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,We truly regret it,\Nand would like to offer our sincerest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:15.30,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats didn't kidnap them after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:18.83,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,I knew they couldn't have done it all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.18,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:23.97,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We all thought that they were the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.08,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,N-No, we believed in them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:28.59,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:30.12,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.18,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.49,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,You're being unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.02,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.75,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We must admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:39.59,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We doubted them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:43.16,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We doubted them because they were human!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:47.96,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,That's how it's always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.31,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We've always seen the humans as...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.99,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Super...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.96,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Afro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.22,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Franky-san, that is quite stylish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.24,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Super, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:02.72,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I get completely worn out\Nwhenever I use the Monster Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.96,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,and I can't even walk for two or three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:09.60,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,But... I can still treat your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.35,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Is everyone alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.46,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} aren't alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.92,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Everyone seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.63,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.47,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I used my ultimate technique too, so I'm completely worn out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.47,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Let me rest on your lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:22.93,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Pwease!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.79,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Just sleep on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.17,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,No, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.14,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.43,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,It's the Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.15,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Hody?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.45,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Vander Decken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:44.16,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Father, you must have been worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:46.75,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you're safe -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:55.34,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Everyone!  You can rest easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:58.55,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,These men will no longer be allowed to run wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.70,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Now we can live without worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:10.86,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,I can't believe someone so scary\Nwas in the Fishman District, so close to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.61,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,C-Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:16.09,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,He looks like a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.42,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.52,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:28.59,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:29.87,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.67,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,It's Straw Hat Luffy and Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.37,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Please, help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:39.99,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama won't stop bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:45.31,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama pushed himself too far for our sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:46.36,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:52.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,This is awful!  I've got something to stop the bleeding in my backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.38,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.65,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:59.04,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I'm really worried about our next fight, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.79,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Right, I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:02.86,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I'll move you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:05.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,That's a really freaky doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.95,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,A little to the left... the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:09.78,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Can you save Luffy-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:13.50,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I can stop the bleeding,\Nbut he's already lost so much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:15.03,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,He doesn't have enough left!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.03,0:22:16.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:19.65,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Luffy's the only one in the crew with blood type F.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:20.93,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:23.51,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,There must be someone else with that blood type\Nhere in the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:24.28,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:25.69,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:27.74,Thoughts,Citizen,0,0,0,,I... I've got F.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.59,Thoughts,Citizen,0,0,0,,I have type F, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:32.51,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Daddy, you're type F, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:33.89,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:39.39,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Oh, right!  This country has a law against donating blood to humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:43.65,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What kind of law is that?!  That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:46.41,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Please!  Luffy's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:52.94,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,My blood type is different, but it's still red!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:54.21,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Will that do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:56.73,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Uh, no.  I appreciate the sentiment, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.80,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:02.04,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I know!  There are some human pirates here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:14.21,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Use my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:19.27,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,It's type F.  I'll give you as much as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:20.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:21.56,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Jinbe-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.56,0:23:23.85,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,But, the law...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:27.06,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I'm a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.16,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Boss!  What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:31.18,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jinbe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:32.89,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:36.31,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Jinbe, you{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:38.09,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,It's fine -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:39.48,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Y-Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:45.42,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,What's the problem?  Outdated laws...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:47.09,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,are just curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:10.04,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Jinbe, this'll hurt a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:11.20,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.16,0:24:34.73,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Even when you're hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:45.47,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,even when you're doing the hurting,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.37,0:24:54.46,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,red blood flows through your veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:08.96,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,This thin, tiny tube,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.96,0:25:14.09,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,too small to be considered a path,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.40,0:25:23.46,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,is what breaks through the prejudiced fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.15,0:25:37.95,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,and the battles that tried to\Nwash away blood with more blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.74,0:25:46.34,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,So easily it flows.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:52.01,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,It is not some fleeting vision in the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.03,0:25:57.98,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,but a clearly visible path that leads to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.58,0:26:10.11,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.91,0:26:13.83,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.83,0:26:14.99,Main,The crew,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.99,0:26:16.70,Main,Citizens,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.78,0:26:20.67,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,What, you were conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.13,0:26:25.66,Main,Citizens,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.66,0:26:26.97,Main,Citizens,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.65,0:26:58.29,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,This is... our new beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.01,0:27:03.10,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.63,0:27:19.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.96,0:27:34.82,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.64,0:27:39.23,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,The Royal Family has made its decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.46,0:27:43.74,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Alright!  We're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.40,0:27:46.77,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Serves you right, Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.85,0:27:50.74,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,I thought I'd live the rest of my days as a slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.74,0:27:54.56,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Pirates, we owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.56,0:27:56.89,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.89,0:27:59.04,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Huh?!  I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.04,0:28:00.36,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Idiot!  I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.36,0:28:04.72,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,We can finally go to the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.72,0:28:08.58,Main,Right Minister,0,0,0,,What if their grudge against Hody\Nturns into a grudge against Fishman Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.58,0:28:15.50,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,That shouldn't change my decision.  This island\Nis a rest stop and tourism destination for pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.50,0:28:18.56,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,They didn't come here with ill intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.56,0:28:21.62,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,There is no reason for us to keep them -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.62,0:28:26.05,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Now then, as for the remaining members of\Nthe New Fishman Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.05,0:28:28.33,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,P-Please don't execute us!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.33,0:28:29.81,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,S-Spare our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.81,0:28:35.36,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,We didn't know anything about Hody murdering the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.36,0:28:37.18,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,They're all insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.18,0:28:38.99,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I sentence you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.01,0:28:43.03,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,to live here, on Fishman Island's mainland!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.03,0:28:45.01,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.01,0:28:48.35,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,What?!  You mean to live under the law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.35,0:28:51.12,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,That's fine by me.\NIt's better than being ruled by Hody.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.12,0:28:55.75,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,You can't do that, Your Majesty!\NWe can't let these guys roam the streets freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.75,0:28:58.43,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We'll be scared to let our children out of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.86,0:29:02.93,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Of course, they'll work under my army's command...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.93,0:29:05.54,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,and will be pressed into service -jamon
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.54,0:29:10.89,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I will give them jobs where\Ntheir formidable strength can be put to good use!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.89,0:29:13.38,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,The Fishman District,\Nwhich we cannot watch effectively...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.38,0:29:17.23,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,will be completely closed off\Nfrom this day forward -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.72,0:29:21.85,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The revelation of the true culprit\Nbehind Queen Otohime's assassination...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.85,0:29:25.57,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,has brought the darkness of fishmankind to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.23,0:29:30.01,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Pirate Hody Jones's plot to conquer Fishman Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.51,0:29:36.93,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,was, ironically, foiled by human pirates who had stopped at the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.05,0:29:40.18,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.76,0:29:43.23,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Where is Straw Hat Luffy -jamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.23,0:29:46.37,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,Well, you see... He ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.37,0:29:47.60,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,R-Ran away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.89,0:29:52.56,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,May I ask why you all left the plaza,\Nas if you're trying to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.56,0:29:54.38,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What a stupid thing to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.38,0:29:57.90,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Back there, our fight was staged like a show for the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.90,0:30:01.92,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,If we stayed in the plaza,\Nwe might be made into some kind of heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.92,0:30:04.76,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it makes me shudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.20,0:30:08.44,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,You mean to say that\Nyou don't wish to become heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.44,0:30:15.14,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Listen up!  Heroes are the kind of people\Nwho divide up and share their booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.14,0:30:16.89,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,But I wanna drink all of it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.89,0:30:20.02,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Again, where did you guys get this idea from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.02,0:30:22.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why won't you join us, Jinbe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.28,0:30:24.10,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's go on adventures together!  Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.10,0:30:27.41,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's go out to sea!  It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.41,0:30:29.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Yeah, join our crew, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.60,0:30:32.95,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,A former Warlord in our crew would be really reassuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.95,0:30:35.50,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,And Luffy, you need to rest.  Don't get worked up. {originally: And it would make things safer for Luffy, too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.21,0:30:40.49,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I'm only saying that I can't join you {\i1}yet{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.58,0:30:45.44,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.44,0:30:49.95,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I'm sure it would be fun\Nto travel the seas with all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.50,0:30:54.97,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,but there are still things I must do first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.97,0:31:01.24,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Things that I am honor bound to do.\NI've only taken a short break from those obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.01,0:31:08.09,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I must still complete that journey.\NOnce I am able to move freely again...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.09,0:31:13.23,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,I will come to meet up with you.  This I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.21,0:31:19.37,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,If you still feel the same way when that time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.37,0:31:24.01,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,will you invite me to join once more,\NStraw Hat Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.01,0:31:25.24,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This is a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.45,0:31:35.51,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey, now... When a man is fulfilling his honor,\Nyou shouldn't pressure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.51,0:31:37.30,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It seems Luffy's taken quite a liking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.85,0:31:48.48,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,A friend of Luffy's is a friend of ours!\NWe'll be waiting for you, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.68,0:31:51.79,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.34,0:31:53.98,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.04,0:31:56.38,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Do we just head straight for the New World?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.99,0:32:01.04,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Are you saying that you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.04,0:32:05.41,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you properly,\Nand spend some more time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.41,0:32:10.40,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Okay, then!  Let's spend at least a week in\Nthe Mermaid Café before we leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.40,0:32:12.99,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You think we don't know\Nthe real reason why you want to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.99,0:32:14.26,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Granted, I completely agree with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.24,0:32:16.96,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Hey!  Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.68,0:32:19.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.33,0:32:21.66,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Isn't that a soldier from the Neptune Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.66,0:32:24.06,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Please hold on, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.50,0:32:27.27,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,King Neptune, I've caught up with the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.27,0:32:29.89,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Good.  Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.89,0:32:31.49,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Why did you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.49,0:32:32.45,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,We still haven't thanked{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.45,0:32:34.51,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.51,0:32:37.54,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I understand that.\NI just wanted to invite you to a feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.54,0:32:40.41,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Let us resume the feast\Nthat was interrupted before -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.41,0:32:41.83,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,A feast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.83,0:32:45.37,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright!  Let's go call Hachi, Caimie and the others too!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.23,0:32:53.12,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,On Neptune's orders,\Nthe Fishman District was immediately sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.15,0:33:01.32,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hody, as well as the New Fishman Pirates' commanders and Vander Decken,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.32,0:33:04.12,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,were all locked away in the prison tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.60,0:33:12.03,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Kraken!  Take him to a distant sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.03,0:33:15.56,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Wadatsumi, there's no cell big enough for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.56,0:33:19.13,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,You are banished from this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.55,0:33:21.81,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Did you find any?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.81,0:33:23.50,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.50,0:33:26.85,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Alright, let's cook 'em up\Nand bring 'em all to Ryuuguu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.85,0:33:29.94,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,They've invited the Straw Hats to a huge feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.94,0:33:31.22,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We'll handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.73,0:33:34.28,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,We heard that sea monster meat is their favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.68,0:33:37.23,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Let's bring them candy and cakes too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.23,0:33:39.05,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,I heard that they can eat a ton of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.05,0:33:40.36,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Bring everything you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.36,0:33:44.44,Main,Citizen,0,0,0,,Do we have enough alcohol?  We'll give 'em\Nso much top shelf liquor they could bathe in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.73,0:33:48.08,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun and his crew,\NI'm glad you could come -jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.08,0:33:50.70,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,That being said, we can speak at the feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.14,0:33:54.09,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,The long flounders will carry you to the banquet hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.38,0:33:56.64,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Whoa, those are some huge rays!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.64,0:33:57.66,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,They're flounders.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.66,0:33:59.66,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Don't you listen, Luffy?\NHe just said that they were flounders.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.49,0:34:07.82,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It's a pitch-black, flooded room...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.82,0:34:11.21,Main,Caimie,0,0,0,,I never thought someone like me\Nwould see Ryuuguu Palace.  I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.52,0:34:14.59,Main,Hachi,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've been in Ryuuguu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.59,0:34:16.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where are we?  Where's the meat and feast?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.13,0:34:20.35,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,Oh!  Our heroes have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.17,0:34:25.01,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,The floor's covered with soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.01,0:34:30.69,Main,Guard,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heroes!  Heroes!  Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.69,0:34:33.75,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Shut up!  Quit saying we're heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.75,0:34:35.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm eating all the meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.01,0:34:39.10,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,That's right!  I wanna drink all the booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.07,0:34:42.27,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You're both hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.64,0:34:46.10,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, the stage is right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.72,0:34:49.96,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.10,0:34:53.31,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,First off, let me introduce the pride of Fishman Island, the number one diva on the ocean floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.31,0:34:55.35,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,Maria Napole!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.06,0:35:36.94,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,And the Swing Jazz Orchestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.01,0:35:50.48,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What an amazing singing voice! {Eh, I've heard better. Oh, and for the record, the song lyrics are not included in the CCs and are just about unintelligible... So no subtitles for u.}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.48,0:35:52.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Maria-sama! {not sure what he's saying before "Maria-sama" --Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.60,0:35:55.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My soul is trembling!  Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.09,0:36:07.78,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,And our special guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.80,0:36:10.30,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.96,0:36:20.64,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,Men are left breathless by their beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.24,0:36:37.10,Main,Voice,0,0,0,,The Mermaid Café Dancers!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.68,0:36:47.70,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.20,0:36:58.95,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You'll die, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.99,0:37:04.38,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Beauty too pure to be captured by a mere picture!\NThese ladies are number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.82,0:37:08.71,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,My powuh ith fadibg...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.71,0:37:09.51,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.51,0:37:10.68,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.68,0:37:11.77,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Simply spellbinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.18,0:37:15.96,Main,Ishilly,0,0,0,,Caimie!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.96,0:37:18.91,Main,Caimie,0,0,0,,Ishilly!  You're alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.73,0:37:25.50,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Finally!  Can't have a feast without this!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.35,0:37:29.36,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I've been super-waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.36,0:37:31.11,Main,Pappagg,0,0,0,,I'd expect no less from Ryuuguu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.17,0:37:33.00,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.77,0:37:34.68,Main,Jinbe,0,0,0,,Most obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.15,0:37:35.95,Main,Princes,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.24,0:37:38.90,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mermaid-chaaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.62,0:37:43.94,Main,Princess,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.08,0:37:48.01,Main,Everyone,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.01,0:37:50.52,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Now, let's start drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.65,0:37:54.89,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.89,0:37:56.35,Main,Mermad,0,0,0,,You can have as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.35,0:37:58.28,Thoughts,Sanji,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.28,0:37:59.88,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.16,0:38:05.16,Main,Mermaid,0,0,0,,You should be more careful, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.96,0:38:07.64,Main,Shirahoshi,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.64,0:38:08.80,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.31,0:38:10.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.99,0:38:14.41,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Cheers -jamon!  It's alright -jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.01,0:38:18.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You guys too!  Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.16,0:38:19.26,Main,Guards,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.98,0:38:22.75,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,This drink is quite delicious.\NIs it made using different water?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.75,0:38:25.88,Main,Left Minister,0,0,0,,Oh, so you can tell the difference, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.64,0:38:29.70,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Refill!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.70,0:38:33.06,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What's with the pale faces?  My cup's empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.06,0:38:35.56,Main,Fukaboshi,0,0,0,,W-We lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.68,0:38:40.67,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Akkamanbo!  Fuuri!  Fuuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.67,0:38:43.19,Main,Manboshi,0,0,0,,Keep dancing, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.19,0:38:46.93,Main,Ryuuboshi,0,0,0,,Eat, drink, and let loose -mi fa so la ti do!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.47,0:39:05.15,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about -jamon,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.15,0:39:06.05,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Pirate girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.56,0:39:10.28,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Forgive me.  I thought this would be\Nour best chance to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.90,0:39:16.00,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I-I should make this clear, I have sworn to love nobody but my wife, Otohime, for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.00,0:39:18.84,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,She might be dead now, but I could never betray{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.84,0:39:20.66,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Who is Joyboy?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.54,0:39:29.14,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I read a Poneglyph in the Sea Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.29,0:39:32.09,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Who was he apologizing to?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.61,0:39:37.34,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,You can read them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.48,0:39:42.84,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I'm a survivor from Ohara.\NIf you don't want to tell me, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.05,0:39:49.03,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.21,0:39:53.62,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I'll tell you all that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.42,0:39:56.09,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I'm okay with you knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.77,0:40:04.18,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Joyboy was a man from the surface, who lived during the void century.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.18,0:40:07.64,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,So he died at least eight hundred years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.64,0:40:13.61,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,That message was directed to the Mermaid Princess\Nwho had lived on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.56,0:40:19.07,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,It was an apology,\Nbecause he'd broken a promise to Fishman Island. {THAT FOREHEAD! O_O --Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.07,0:40:21.01,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.01,0:40:24.18,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,The details haven't been passed down,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.18,0:40:30.84,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,but eventually somebody will come and carry out the promise in Joyboy's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.84,0:40:34.55,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,That is the legend that is passed down\Nthrough the Royal Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.84,0:40:37.54,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,We promised to believe in that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.54,0:40:43.58,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,and each generation has taken its turn to watch over the Noah, as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.58,0:40:49.81,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,When that day comes,\Nthe Noah will fulfill its mission, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.81,0:40:54.04,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Earlier today,\Nafter everything was finished above the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.04,0:40:57.31,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I heard that the half-destroyed Noah was carried into the Sea Forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.41,0:41:00.52,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,by the Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.03,0:41:07.44,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Maybe Joyboy, who was going to use the Noah, had the power to control the Sea Kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.44,0:41:13.48,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,No, it was the former Mermaid Princess\Nwho had that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.48,0:41:18.22,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I knew it.\NSo, does Princess Shirahoshi have the same power?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.73,0:41:24.41,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,Yes.  I assume that it awakened completely today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.64,0:41:37.56,Main,Neptune,0,0,0,,I can't say I'm happy about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.56,0:41:39.38,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.38,0:41:46.41,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Two years ago, I read a Poneglyph on Sky Island\Nthat told the location of an ancient weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.03,0:41:52.74,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It said that it was here, on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.60,0:41:57.88,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,The Mermaid Princess\Nwho lived in the same era as Joyboy...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.41,0:42:02.32,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Is this what they called her, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.62,0:42:08.26,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Or in other words, Princess Shirahoshi, who carries the same power...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.26,0:42:11.43,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,will also inherit this title.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.79,0:42:16.49,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Her other name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.26,0:42:21.62,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,the ancient weapon...{ Btwb: split this line since there is quite a big pause and it adds dramatic effect }
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.19,0:42:24.72,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Poseidon!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,

